{"tid":576514,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"做咗份工幾年，第一次去歐洲出差","createTime":"2018-03-01T03:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T02:08:14.000Z","uid":46049,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"98f0aef518f052c7195c8bef1d348f9b486eadc2","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"喺某跨國公司做左幾年野, 老細終於派我去愛爾蘭都柏林總部出差,歐洲人真係好hea, 日日返幾粒鐘就收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個天都仲光緊, 所以我都有好多時間周圍行下, 曬下日光玩足大半日, 呢度嘅日頭都幾靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/111714_1803ea3a839c9ad94c120e23e5492e22.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F111714_1803ea3a839c9ad94c120e23e5492e22.JPG&h=4304bd37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/111631_1f11893bba632a98ecaf3e9fef80c56f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F111631_1f11893bba632a98ecaf3e9fef80c56f.JPG&h=8c7cb5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖三一大學, 好有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭有個別名叫Emerald isle, 即係綠寶石島咁解, 成個國家都綠油油,首都都柏林有好多公園, 勁舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/111958_53702adab60ff2ea20d0f0dd9afaaabd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F111958_53702adab60ff2ea20d0f0dd9afaaabd.JPG&h=bf1b33a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度係St. Stephen&rsquo;s Green公園, 喺正市中心, 好多人喺度散步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112029_a7cc73113822af6d2e26ee1f99d47355.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112029_a7cc73113822af6d2e26ee1f99d47355.JPG&h=492938da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行遠小小仲有另一個更大既公園叫Phoenix Park, 可以近距離睇鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112142_37d416b77f46eeb64bde3f2068ff3154.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112142_37d416b77f46eeb64bde3f2068ff3154.JPG&h=2fe9e9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112336_68e40286d33557e1567e7aa445ab33be.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112336_68e40286d33557e1567e7aa445ab33be.JPG&h=ddcd55f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到好近都唔驚人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112449_6da42860990980af047b56fb516627c6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112449_6da42860990980af047b56fb516627c6.JPG&h=fd0a818f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112517_c22b77675ac7eba7059325fddc08e975.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112517_c22b77675ac7eba7059325fddc08e975.JPG&h=88ebf82f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個公園中間有個巨型十字架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎到愛爾蘭緊係要食下fish and chips <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/112611_7f6b206c8d1e15e8c1bc7d0932293ad8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F112611_7f6b206c8d1e15e8c1bc7d0932293ad8.JPG&h=e846cd99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npo住咁多先, 有人睇再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1771e6a8693f428f6d5b345fbb0932f1ace4f95c","tid":576514,"uid":24403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"樓主邊到轉機 ? 想去但唔知邊間airline好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d75981fe81a671b136a78a87dc8830aefe91bb","tid":576514,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  去幾耐呀"},{"pid":"9f446ab44bd0379c749741c766f56ef851efa354","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1771e6a8693f428f6d5b345fbb0932f1ace4f95c","tid":576514,"uid":24403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"樓主邊到轉機 ? 想去但唔知邊間airline好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:38:54.000Z","msg":"我個陣就坐CX去倫敦轉機，但黎緊好似出直航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ca5ba90e1c6753fcd474f1003d867b6e489562","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"85d75981fe81a671b136a78a87dc8830aefe91bb","tid":576514,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  去幾耐呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"兩個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad0a60dc9c9a1bb829381bc92089aa62b46ae56","tid":576514,"uid":73730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前份工，做一年半，出左5-6次trip次次都好辛苦<br />\n有次去芝加哥，-1X度不特止，日日做08-18，夜晚繼續做香港既野<br />\n唉，同trip唔同命"},{"pid":"f7fc8dc8d3afbbfb76cf205c1c3110964e99131b","tid":576514,"uid":30293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"愈睇得多愈感覺香港慘過狗"},{"pid":"b8a435f4ffd94ae9310b33d3e8e8433742b8a7a0","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"上網search都柏林必去景點, 見好多人都推介去Howth遠足, 所以一放假就出發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163624_ec677bd0134cc917737d9612726ff599.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163624_ec677bd0134cc917737d9612726ff599.JPG&h=8bd67535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一早就去坐DART, 都柏林既火車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163625_334fe1a3a2db6787a1e611e59e4622cd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163625_334fe1a3a2db6787a1e611e59e4622cd.JPG&h=070c6d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHowth係都柏林東面既一個半島 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發點有分唔同難度既路線, 我就揀條易既輕輕鬆鬆行下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163829_40b2a6f2775bb85242ef3a69d36cfb68.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163829_40b2a6f2775bb85242ef3a69d36cfb68.JPG&h=2aa9d9d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163830_aec775ac17319fcca3d812e75c23b3b3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163830_aec775ac17319fcca3d812e75c23b3b3.JPG&h=70878178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163831_2ee6d2071d5880f0340b5aff71db8278.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163831_2ee6d2071d5880f0340b5aff71db8278.JPG&h=cf7ddc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個海有唔同顏色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163905_c7368f17fb63238fbb80f0a42c8c04bd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163905_c7368f17fb63238fbb80f0a42c8c04bd.JPG&h=c7fb72f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163906_5cf6f32e9258aebcac976ab35039a479.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163906_5cf6f32e9258aebcac976ab35039a479.JPG&h=73c24182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163907_2818eb22ec98b07ca8a5bab351601972.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163907_2818eb22ec98b07ca8a5bab351601972.JPG&h=499a5841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163929_2818eb22ec98b07ca8a5bab351601972.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163929_2818eb22ec98b07ca8a5bab351601972.JPG&h=e002a2d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/01/163931_dc705f93bb1051fe6dcea6b246cb9de0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F163931_dc705f93bb1051fe6dcea6b246cb9de0.JPG&h=e7f82c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吸到空氣都爽到暈"},{"pid":"11c94e210e22518ca632aca0cb2b58f7eed65444","tid":576514,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"咁好天?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3334e84ed8444050998feeeb1c386030954b9ed0","tid":576514,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好靚啊<br />\n樓主咩行業？我都想返。"},{"pid":"bf1a3dd77fecc4071f497f9a81b17b095485a06a","tid":576514,"uid":73788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:37:14.000Z","msg":"啲景J死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae53c34097fa3c0d9c0f6ff1056d68eca1c7a8e","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ad0a60dc9c9a1bb829381bc92089aa62b46ae56","tid":576514,"uid":73730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"之前份工，做一年半，出左5-6次trip次次都好辛苦<br />\n有次去芝加哥，-1X度不特止，日日做08-18，夜晚繼續做香港既野<br />\n唉，同trip唔同命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"我都係咁岩好彩去愛爾蘭咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c618fdaedb776787a5848a6343d3a21bf7d575f","tid":576514,"uid":144769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d6c540b773ea6fc0c8a5a2256242c00b1c071ce","tid":576514,"uid":29150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"出差幾耐？ 有weekend 比你玩咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2d2a0cabccfe7f60efe470bf174fdfe8ea3528","tid":576514,"uid":46049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7fc8dc8d3afbbfb76cf205c1c3110964e99131b","tid":576514,"uid":30293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"愈睇得多愈感覺香港慘過狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"一返到香港，個種清新空氣真係無曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ea3e48b596dbc5a945db5f9b5fed7945f33102","tid":576514,"uid":80696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T11:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\